   What's New
   [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif] [spacer.gif]
   [spacer.gif] Project Perfect
   APPL's innovative two-day training workshop-board game simulates an
   accelerated project life cycle. Played out in a visual model of
   "Provide Aerospace Products and Capabilities," Project Perfect is a
   highly competitive way of test-driving your project planning skills.

   Project Mirror
   This new and improved course is not just a training event, but also a
   rigorous five-day program of highly individualized assessment that
   offers an effective new way of measuring and developing your project
   management skills.
